---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>About Nairatoday</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about Nairatoday, a financial technology platform providing up-to-date Naira exchange rates, digital tools, and market insights." />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="about-page">
      <h1>About Nairatoday</h1>
      <p>
        <b>Nairatoday</b> (<a href="https://nairatoday.com">nairatoday.com</a>) is a financial technology project aimed at providing up-to-date <b>Naira exchange rates</b>, digital tools, and market insights for users in Nigeria and worldwide.
      </p>
      <h2>Black Market Exchange Rates</h2>
      <p>
        Nairatoday majorly covers the Nigerian Black Market rates, also known as the Parallel Market, Bureau De Change (BDC), and Foreign Exchange (FX) Markets. We help you track real rates, not just official figures.
      </p>
      <h2>Official Exchange Rates</h2>
      <p>
        On Nairatoday, you can also find the official exchange rate of the Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN) and leading foreign exchange markets.
      </p>
      <h2>Western Union and MoneyGram</h2>
      <p>
        Our API provides the current exchange rates for Western Union and MoneyGram, offering accurate rates for these popular remittance services.
      </p>
      <h2>Nigerian Banks’ Rates</h2>
      <p>
        We provide insights on the exchange rates of major Nigerian banks—including GTBank, Ecobank, Access Bank, Zenith Bank, and more.
      </p>
      <h2>Cryptocurrency Exchange Rates</h2>
      <p>
        As Nigerians embrace cryptocurrency, we aggregate data from platforms like Bittrex, Bitfinex, Luno, Coinbase, and Poloniex, providing updates on Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, Cardano, IOTA, Ripple, and more.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top:1.7em; background:#e6f4ea; padding:1em 1.3em; border-radius:9px; color:#2b483b;">
        <b>Note:</b> The figures provided here are for guidance only. Rates may vary as currency values fluctuate by the minute.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
